body:
`near` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
   $search: {
      "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
      "near": {
         "path": "<field-to-search>",
         "origin": <date-or-number>,
         "pivot": <pivot-distance>,
         "score": <score-options>
      }
   }
}
```
